{"tid":2444812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係美國一早打死你班黑暴啦","createTime":"2021-03-13T06:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T19:20:06.000Z","uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"768c71aa80eb9e6e3ff13670a68e94784632af1c","tid":2444812,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"BLM｜美國明尼阿波利斯市與弗洛伊德家人達成和解 賠償逾$2億<br />\n<br />\n美國黑人弗洛伊德（George Floyd）去年5月被警員跪頸致死，明尼阿波利斯（Minneapolis）市政府跟弗洛伊德家人在周五達成和解，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">作出2,700萬美元（約2.1億港元）賠償，成為美國史上涉及死亡的民權事件中最大和解金額。</span></span></strong>而跪頸的前警員喬文（Derek Chauvin）被加控3級謀殺罪名，他繼續否認指控，審訊進入遴選陪審團的階段，料不會遲於3月29日開庭審訊。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">涉案前警員被加控3級謀殺 最遲3月底開審</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n跪頸的前警員喬文周四被加控3級謀殺，連同之前被控的2級非蓄意殺人和2級誤殺，合共面臨3罪指控，他否認全部控罪。去年5月案發後，喬文起初被控3級謀殺，同年10月遭法官卡希爾（Peter Cahil）駁回，認為該罪名不適合用於這宗案件。州上訴庭上周下令卡希爾重新考慮批准有關指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210313/MBRJCU6BRNC5RALA5G4C2ROECM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2awrsLaTTAd9HLCB8r9FZZKjuk2IlRrtUhCG-xzl2q7v_b0bSdDeDrpkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2FMBRJCU6BRNC5RALA5G4C2ROECM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2awrsLaTTAd9HLCB8r9FZZKjuk2IlRrtUhCG-xzl2q7v_b0bSdDeDrpkc&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=da22edb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210313%2FMBRJCU6BRNC5RALA5G4C2ROECM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2awrsLaTTAd9HLCB8r9FZZKjuk2IlRrtUhCG-xzl2q7v_b0bSdDeDrpkc&h=245e1a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/internationa